708048f-a.title: Manhattan: 3rd Avenue - 35th Street (East)
708048f-a.text:
Third Ave., at and adjoining the S.W. corner of 35th Street. Also
shown is 35th Street, south side, west from Third Ave., to, but not in-
cluding Lexington Aves. No. 522 Third Ave., at the S.W. corner of 35th
Street, is a 3-story frame house. No. 162 East 35th Street, west of
Third Ave., is a 2-story frame building also. The view shows the
25th Precinct Police Station at No. 160 East 35th Street, west of the S.W.
corner of Third Ave.
July 23, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

708045f-a.title: Manhattan: 3rd Avenue - 35th Street (East)
708045f-a.text:
Third Avenue, west side, north from E. 35th Street.

Crystal Buildings.
January 7, 1939
